{"tid":1417974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議] 下星期五六日連續三日入機場和你飛","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:19:11.000Z","uid":38737,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2060e225d0aeb041010733029805dc0be2f8df2c","tid":1417974,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:05.000Z","msg":"睇完林鄭垃圾記招<br />\n香港人一定會繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEaW2uw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEaW2uw.jpg&h=39236704&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n照返香港人日程表<br />\n<strong>810輪到黃大仙、大埔</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>811輪到深水埗、港島東</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n其實連繽兩個星期嘅六日都有遊行／集會（元朗－＞上環－＞旺角－＞西環＋將軍澳）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上全部都係勇武回合<br />\n然後都係同一個劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行－＞堵路／圍狗屋－＞死守／轉場－＞狗射TG／開槍－＞畜龍鳩衝－＞義士受傷／跑唔切被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得接下來呢一星期應該係真．和理非回合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以大膽建議<br />\n下星期六日<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩日嘅遊行取消</span></strong><br />\n連埋星期五一於<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連續三日入機場和你飛</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順帶一提其實由730開始已經開始有同路人入機場，TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=708e1070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n<br />\n原因如下：<br />\n1. 心水清都知唔同地方搞遊行都係想開發新戰場，但85已經試過晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 726和你飛做得幾好幾成功大家有目共睹，機場亦係一個好地方（有冷氣、廁所、wifi等等）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 勇武咗咁多日，係時候休息下（變身做和理非）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 完全符合運動嘅原則：不受傷不被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好重要嘅原因其實下面兩個post都講咗，唔重覆了<br />\n<br />\n如果真係識玩嘅，今晚之後暫停一陣勇武抗爭！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416146</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最近真係打得太密, 我有野想講下, 希望大家可以望望<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n歡迎發表意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaaf6d1671af61e403823a8fda819ec506dbe60d","tid":1417974,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:40:04.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e0c5037f584655726c00dcbcd4ca77863ccc9cad","tid":1417974,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"正所謂一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而歇<br />\n宣布咗會遊行就唔好取消啦，取消完要再聚是不容易的<br />\n不過樓主不是完全沒有道理，所以大家呢兩次遊行完咗就回家吧，不要死守戀戰走唔切被告近止。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbdd249170c99c694c8e84bc88c35fffd14bb75","tid":1417974,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:13:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4202176dc96a4230d72daa73ddf8ac39cdf22e1","tid":1417974,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:14:24.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n目的唔係分化p牌會員<br />\n而係當你見到有大量p牌洗正負評時<br />\n要比平時更小心去做決定"},{"pid":"3d63f20bef092b5931dca4ed418b1cb793cc9f2d","tid":1417974,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:00:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f20deba07d9fe2fa9054a328e6cf7edb7017d41e","tid":1417974,"uid":39568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong>推晒所有機場post<br />\n8月9-11日<br />\n和理非進場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFeQsAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFeQsAz.jpg&h=ead62688&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a68409c8f9ab23ef643c089b6584cfa842f86e73","tid":1417974,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f20deba07d9fe2fa9054a328e6cf7edb7017d41e","tid":1417974,"uid":39568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong>推晒所有機場post<br />\n8月9-11日<br />\n和理非進場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFeQsAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFeQsAz.jpg&h=ead62688&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}